309	introduction	<div>Welcome to Ithuta Books! </div><div> </div><div>We give learners the tools to master all the <strong>terms and concepts of maths and science</strong>.</div><div> </div><div><em>Many maths and science learners proceed too soon to the application / problem-solving step, assuming (incorrectly) that their theory knowledge is fine and that they understand the terms and concepts fully. Do you see that in your child / yourself?</em></div><div> </div><div>To succeed in maths and science, learners must <strong>understand the maths / science terms</strong> and develop<strong> the concepts</strong>. They must also <strong>revise their foundations</strong> to master previous years’ concepts, as each year builds on the knowledge of the previous years. </div><div> </div><div>Each dictionary covers many years of curriculum, therefore catering for a learner’s current work and that of previous years, in which the learner’s background may not be 100%.</div><div> </div><div>Using our maths and science explanatory dictionaries, learners will cover all three of these requirements: <strong>terms, concepts, revision</strong> <strong>of theory</strong>. </div><div><strong><em> </em></strong></div><div><strong><em>HOW CAN WE HELP? </em></strong></div><div>Use <strong>“UNDERSTAND MATHS AND SCIENCE” EXPLANATORY DICTIONARIES</strong>.</div><div><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMTc4MD9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--ad39f6538bc98244cbb63bbf0ba09fbcce251624" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdlFHIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--153c6813340594727cfc088c316c16f723343878/How%20to%20Study%20using%20dict.png" filename="How to Study using dict.png" filesize="162712" width="1074" height="666" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachm