225	about	<div><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMzE1MD9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--2d85205dec531c7a2533d23f62bbe1bf3e31a9fb" content-type="image/png" url="http://www.homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBazRNIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--dd44b24ee75908539b8e856abfcc694a9f583ae3/workshop.png" filename="workshop.png" filesize="2451639" width="1630" height="865" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Business Simulator"></action-text-attachment></div><h1><strong>Business Simulation</strong></h1><div><br>The goal of business simulation / decision-making games is to give participants the opportunity to create and manage their virtual businesses by means of gamification.</div><div> </div><div><strong>How does it work?</strong></div><ul><li>In these decision games, participants of your course will set up and manage virtual companies. How does it work?</li><li>Teams will start virtual companies.</li><li>Teams members run their companies making realistic business decisions.</li><li>Virtual companies compete with other virtual businesses in one market.</li><li>Teams analyse market results, draw conclusions, solve business problems.</li><li>There is no single right answer, each game is a real entrepreneurship training for the players.</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>What is the value of business simulation for learners?</strong></div><ul><li>Intuitive and user-friendly</li><li>Improve teamwork and decision-making skills</li><li>Improve time management </li><li>Boost engagement and motivation to study</li><li>Can be done 24/7/365 </li><li>Realistic business decisions in a selected market</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>Advantages for parents</strong></div><ul><li>Educational innovation focused on learner development that distinguishes home learners from learners at school.</li><li>A modern method of training called hybrid learning.</li><li>Increased learner involvement through healthy teamwork and competition.</li><li>Study material/methods that the parent enjoys.</li><li>The parent becomes more than an educator, and also a mentor.</li><li>Parents, peers, siblings and teachers can participate as a team (promoting teamwork)</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>Simulation Industries learners can choose from</strong></div><ul><li>Entertainment</li><li>Travel</li><li>Hair salon</li><li>Shipping company</li><li>IT Company</li></ul><div><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMzE0OD9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--bc24c7a7b0698a05c5162fb0791abfc7dd69de60" content-type="image/jpeg" url="http://www.homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBa3dNIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--b2e84722fac28f9abe09d85e49dd2db171b6385b/image001.jpg" filename="image001.jpg" filesize="146250" width="1700" height="822" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Travel Agency"></action-text-attachment><br><br></div><h1><strong>Besigheidsimulasie</strong></h1><div> </div><div>Die doel van besigheidsimulasie / besluitnemings-speletjies is om deelnemers die geleentheid te gee om hulle virtuele besighede te stig en te bestuur</div><div> </div><div><strong>Hoe werk dit in die praktyk?</strong></div><ul><li>Elke span stig / skep 'n afsonderlike virtuele maatskappy.</li><li>Spanne bestuur elk sy eie maatskappy deur besigheidsbesluite te neem.</li><li>Daar word vir kliënte gekompeteer in een marksegment</li><li>Spanne analiseer mark resultate, en los besigheidsprobleme op.</li></ul><div> </div><div>Daar is geen absolute korrekte antwoord nie (die wins / verlies is die aanwysers). Elke spel is entrepreneurs-opleiding vir die deelnemers.</div><div> </div><div><strong>Wat is die waarde van Besigheidsimulasie vir leerders?</strong></div><ul><li>Intuitief en gebruikersvriendelik</li><li>Verbeter Spanwerk en Besluitnemingsvaardighede</li><li>Verbeter tydsbestuur</li><li>Verbeter betrokkenheid en motivering om the studeer</li><li>24/7/365 beskikbaarheid</li><li>Realistiese besigheids besluite in 'n geslekteerde mark</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>Voordele vir Ouers</strong></div><ul><li>Opvoedkundige innovasie wat tuisskolers van publieke skole onderskei deurdat dit op leerderontwikkeling fokus</li><li>'n Moderne metode van opleiding ganaamd hibriede leer.</li><li>Verhoogde leerder-betrokkenheid deur gesonde spanwerk en kompetisie.</li><li>Studiemateriaal / metodes wat pret vir die leerkrag is.</li><li>Die ouer word meer as opvoeder, ook mentor</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>Simulasie Industriëe waaruit leerders kan kies</strong></div><ul><li>Vermaaklikheid</li><li>Reisburo</li><li>Haarsalon</li><li>Skeepsvrag</li><li>IT Maatskappy</li></ul><div><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMzE0OT9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--c7d518766df923c49ba7bd5b060ce8bc818f9402" content-type="image/jpeg" url="http://www.homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBazBNIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--bea5bd0e42f3c421ef4e12831d93eb3ffb1be29a/image002.jpg" filename="image002.jpg" filesize="167001" width="1702" height="825" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Travel Agency"></action-text-attachment></div>	Workshop	5	2020-09-21 20:44:50.405971	2020-10-13 09:09:19.855031
