198	apply_faq_exhibitor	<div><strong>This FAQ's guide consists of five sections:</strong></div><ul><li><strong>A few general FAQ's, some of which was already mentioned in the FAQ's that accompanied the Prospectus and Application Form to Exhibit. </strong></li><li><strong>A guide that will assist you step by step to complete the setup of your company's exhibition stall.</strong></li><li><strong>A guide on how to interact with visitors during the expo.</strong></li><li><strong>Advertisement dimensions for the PDF Expo program for those of you that are advertising in the Expo Program.</strong></li><li><strong>Things that we will need from you if you have ordered the “Personal Stall Designer” option, where we have to setup your stall on your behalf.</strong></li></ul><div><br></div><h1>1. General FAQ's</h1><div><strong>What are the starting and ending times of the expo?</strong></div><ul><li>The expo will start at Tuesday 13 October 2020 at 09:00 and will end on Saturday 17 October at 24:00.</li></ul><div><strong>Is it compulsory to exhibit for the entire duration of the expo?</strong></div><ul><li>Although exhibitor monitoring of the stall for the complete duration of the expo is not required, we recommend that the exhibitor will be available from 8:00 to 17:00 on expo days to answer visitor enquiries. When you are not available, visitors will still be able to leave you a message. If you are available after hours, you can encourage visitor enquiries, by putting a notice on your stall.</li></ul><div><strong>What is the difference between a Webcam Interview and a Speaker Session?</strong></div><ul><li>Presentations at the expo will provide an online equivalent to speaker sessions in an auditorium at a physical event.</li><li>The Presentations page will contain three types of presentations:<ul><li><strong>Featured Presentations:</strong> Topical presentations by keynote speakers arranged by the organisers. </li><li><strong>Webcam Interviews:</strong> Bouwe van der Eems, from SA Homeschoolers, will do a recorded interview with you via Zoom or GoTo Meeting before the expo. Apart from it being available on the Presentations page you can will be able use it for marketing and to also display it as one of the video's in your stall.</li><li><strong>Speaker Session:</strong> This is a video-recorded speaker presentation of which the production is your responsibility. Although you may use this opportunity to promote your Products and Services, from experience on what people tend to listen to, we recommend a topical approach that has the benefit of confirming you or your company as an authority on the subject. In the description you can link back to the stall. You can also use this video as one of your videos at your stall. The suggested length for the video is not more than half an hour.</li></ul></li><li>All presentations will be viewable throughout the duration of the expo.  </li></ul><div><br></div><h1>2. Setting up your online stall</h1><ul><li>When setting up your stall please save regularly.</li><li>If you have more than one staff member that will assist in setting up the stall, avoid doing it at the same time, since saving may overwrite each others changes.</li><li>To add more staff members scroll down to Manage Stall Staff at the end of this section. </li><li>To view how the information that you have entered and saved appears on your stall, click on Exhibitors in the menu bar, scroll down to your stall and click on Show.   </li></ul><div><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvNDI3P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--f96237fb8ddc4e1ecffdc1ae5ff69daa1edf836c" content-type="image/png" url="http://www.homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcXNCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--3ae0150d4c810b80b192785d1e07d03afce96264/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="6019" width="1123" height="48" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment><strong>General Details – Tab<br></strong><br></div><ul><li><strong>The Flipcard Discription:</strong><ul><li>This short description appears on the flip side of your Exhibitor Index Card on the <a href="http://www.homeschoolexpo.africa/events/1/exhibitors">Exhibitors page</a>. </li><li>It provides for approximately 50 words - after you have completed and saved this field check the card to ensure that the contents fit on the card.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Flipcard Banner:</strong><ul><li>This banner appears on the flip side of your Exhibitor Index Card on the <a href="http://www.homeschoolexpo.africa/events/1/exhibitors">Exhibitors page</a> along with your company logo.</li><li>Supported file types are JPEG, JPG, PNG or a GIF throughout the website.</li><li>Recommended dimensions: 400 x 250 pixels (W x H). </li><li>Maximum file size: 200 KB.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Avatar: </strong><ul><li>The circular image that appears on your Flipcard Banner and your Stall Banner.</li><li>This is usually your company logo.</li><li>Recommended dimensions: 300 x 300 pixels (W x H). </li><li>Maximum file size: 150 KB.</li><li>Leave enough of a image margin to ensure that your image displays correctly - you may have to experiment a bit.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Stall Banner:</strong><ul><li>This banner will be displayed at the top of your stall page.</li><li>Recommended dimensions: 2000 x 500 pixels (W x H). </li><li>Maximum file size: 250 KB.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Stall liaison person:</strong><ul><li>This is the email and telephone number for the person that arranged for the stall on behalf of your company - in contrast to the contact details on the Let's Chart Tab, this information will not be visible to visitors.</li><li>By default this person will be created as the first stall member that will also have the ability to add other stall staff members.</li></ul></li></ul><div><br></div><div><strong>Introduction – Tab</strong><br><br></div><ul><li>With this introduction you can welcome visitors with some opening remarks on your value proposition, what your company is offering and anything else you deem fit to impress the visitor. </li><li>The text editor for entering your information, that you encounter here for the first time, will also be available at a number of other places during the setup. It has basic editing tools that enables you to determine the character of your stall. It makes it possible for you to add video's, pictures, links to additional sources and documents such as brochures and presentations to be downloaded by visitors. Here are a few tips in utilizing the editor:<ul><li><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMzk2P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--6b9a56332436ac7b1392e7c60d84807a297d36f5" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBb3dCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--068f0654b5d2cac3f963b38579a07fc003f58081/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="545" width="45" height="35" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment>You can use this tool to add links to text or if you want to put in links to external websites.</li><li><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMzk3P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--6215506610cb53bb782e6ffb31fdd03e03881b35" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbzBCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--3baefa3d9d4ec643a8994df4f04be83617964447/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="478" width="45" height="32" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment>You can use this tool to add any file from your computer to the text block.</li><li>There are unfortunately not an option to change the font color, but you can make an image in e.g. Canva and add it to the text block. Like in this example:</li><li><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMzk5P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--e1c5f027ead29a3169e68d2cc4f701a754523504" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbzhCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--32f94e398653df0c418808c6f04b53742b84c861/image%20(4).png" filename="image (4).png" filesize="16086" width="642" height="233" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment></li></ul></li></ul><div><strong>Products and Services – Tab<br></strong><br></div><ul><li>Here you can describe your Products and Services with photo’s and text.</li></ul><div><br></div><div><strong>Videos – Tab<br></strong><br></div><ul><li><strong>Video text Field</strong>:<ul><li>You may want to share some introductory information on the video's with the visitor before they viewing the video's start say something and it is exactly for this requirement that we have provided.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Videos</strong>:<ul><li>You can list up to 10 video's.</li><li>To add videos, click on the green Add Videos button and completing the fields.</li><li>You can add a caption to every video.</li><li>In the Path field you can paste the last part of a Youtube video e.g. the part between the quotation marks in this example: <a href="https://youtu.be/q5IGHJ5EyzU">https://youtu.be/<strong>"</strong>q5IGHJ5EyzU</a><strong>"</strong></li></ul></li></ul><div><br><strong>Gallery – Tab<br></strong><br></div><ul><li><strong>Gallery text field:</strong><ul><li>This is a similar field to the Video text field.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Gallery:</strong><ul><li>You can display up to 20 photos.</li><li>To add a new photo’s, click on the green button that says, Add Images.</li><li>Click on Choose File to upload a photo from your computer or replace an already uploaded photo.</li><li>Recommended dimensions: 800 x 500 pixels (W x H). </li><li>Maximum file size: 250 KB.</li><li>You can add a caption to every photo.</li></ul></li></ul><div><br></div><div><strong>About (Exhibiter/Stall) – Tab<br></strong><br></div><ul><li>Self explanatory.</li></ul><div><br><strong>Let's Chat – Tab<br></strong><br></div><ul><li><strong>Contact details:</strong><ul><li>The details on this tab is for the sales person and will be displayed in your stall and in the PDF Program Expo as your company contact details. </li></ul></li><li><strong>Chatra ID:</strong><ul><li>We use the Chatra application to enable visitors to chat with you during the expo or to leave a message if you are not available. </li><li>It is however necessary to register for your own account at Chatra - the free version is adequate.</li><li>Follow these steps to register your account and to obtain the code that has to be entered in the Chatra ID field:<ul><li>Go to <a href="https://chatra.com/">https://chatra.com/</a></li><li>Then click on Sign Up (in Right corner) or if you already have an account with Chatra you can Sign In:<action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvNDEwP2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--4230d275c158d3d0e06bda841e2e356e24094c0a" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcG9CIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--b7b967976d33632c2c783058d233770488fffc71/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="4262" width="411" height="93" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment></li><li>Here you fill in your email address and click on “Let’s go!”: <action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvNDEyP2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--6f54b6696eadb69988e73c84de119b09e600f948" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcHdCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--222406b71145da11ea79a0cf41f8e4545d5738a7/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="33807" width="602" height="415" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment>You will get an email to setup a password for your account. You can also decide whether you want the free version (You are on a free trial (10 days) period of the Pro plan. Once it is over, you will be automatically switched to the Free plan.) or the paid version.</li><li>After you created your account and are logged in, you go to the sidebar on the left: <action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvNDE0P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--bd4ee50be5ab47a46f795334415ff31f5740c72a" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcDRCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--31862f0662d08661872c7983a7e87c9e461e3519/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="30923" width="155" height="525" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment></li><li>Under the tab Channels, you click on the Chat Widget: <action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvNDE1P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--9b744563869efb83f08fa8bb380826e0269b1e04" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcDhCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--d4b5b62fc15ec2ee449012b35ccdf86722cfa6dd/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="7186" width="277" height="192" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment></li><li>Then this page shows. You copy the highlighted text in the HTML block: <action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvNDE2P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--7849ee72144dfe2043159048111b0ddd9975f705" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcUFCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--1229acfb62af2d112abef86bf062b81fef681233/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="44572" width="571" height="246" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment></li><li>Paste the highlighted text in the Chatra ID field. <action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvNDE4P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--c7dbbe71c1ed6f2614681f340e27ae0ab5d58ce1" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcUlCIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--856e239ff8bdee150636e5210d80b4ab84faf941/image.png" filename="image.png" filesize="7006" width="537" height="73" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="."></action-text-attachment></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><strong>Social Media</strong><ul><li>You may add your Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and LinkedIn URL's here.</li><li>Make sure to include "https://" in the link.</li></ul></li></ul><div><strong>Side Bar Info – Tab<br><br></strong>The information on this tab will enable visitors to find your stall when doing searches according to their specific needs.</div><ul><li><strong>Country List:</strong><ul><li>Select the countries where your Products