202	products_and_services	<div>Al die Lomi produkte word ontwikkel om op 'n prettige manier leer moontlik te maak. Die produkte is digitaal beskikbaar en kan of direk by my bestel word (info@lomi.co.za) of via die <a href="https://teachingresources.co.za/vendors/lomi/">https://teachingresources.co.za/vendors/lomi/</a> platform. <br><br><em>All the Lomi products are developed to make learning fun. The digital products are available directly from me (</em><a href="mailto:info@lomi.co.za"><em>info@lomi.co.za</em></a><em>) or via the </em><a href="https://teachingresources.co.za/vendors/lomi/"><em>https://teachingresources.co.za/vendors/lomi/</em></a><em> platform. </em><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMTI2Nj9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--4a13528e17e3e6eccf85caa583defb813924d8bf" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdklFIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e9de6426b4441907466e433cdd3b025f54fa3b5a/Sommer%20pret.png" filename="Sommer pret.png" filesize="72656" width="344" height="307" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Somme(r) Pret reeks"></action-text-attachment><br>Die idee agter die <a href="https://lomi.co.za/sommer-pret-reeks/">Somme(r) Pret reeks</a>  is om wiskunde lekker te maak vir kinders. Kinders moenie ‘n boek gebruik en dink “ek moet” alles kan doen of dat dit eintlik op jonger kinders gerig is nie. Dit is veronderstel om pret te wees - om vir kinders te wys dat wiskunde nie vervelig is nie. Om daardie rede is daar geen graad aan elke boek gekoppel nie.<br>Elke boek het egter ‘n klompie vaardighede in wat op ‘n spesifieke graad gemik is. Die reeks is egter daar om kinders te help om basiese vaardighede op ‘n prettige manier in te oefen. Elke boek in die reeks het ook aktiwiteite in wat nie binne die kurrikulum val nie en wat daarop gemik is om probleem oplossing aan te moedig. <br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMTI2Nz9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--ca9d04f488f68a52feaaed090ca7855f1e5221d9" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdk1FIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--828f4896d559a1bd12a9dec574d61f622632b14b/Pretpakke.png" filename="Pretpakke.png" filesize="261516" width="1080" height="471" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Pretpakke"></action-text-attachment><br><br>Naas die Somme(r) Pret reeks is daar ook 'n verskeidenheid <strong>aktiwiteitspakke </strong>rondom spesifieke temas (soos lente, robotte, ens.) en ook <strong>speletjiepakke. Hierdie pretpakke kan by enige wiskunde kurrikulum gevoeg word om rondom die eentonigheid van werkvelle te werk. <br><br></strong><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMTI2NT9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--61b0e57b675cb924a10cda910439cc60e530d21b" content-type="image/jpeg" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdkVFIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--758c6a1abf1851df15a11a748c8e18cc491c861e/Collages9.jpg" filename="Collages9.jpg" filesize="151517" width="800" height="389" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Kolle-kuiken kry 'n gesin eboek"></action-text-attachment><a href="https://lomi.co.za/kolle-kuiken/"><strong><br>Kolle-Kuiken kry 'n Gesin</strong></a><strong> is 'n e-boek met 'n storie geskryf rondom 'n kolganskuiken wat ons gesin groot gemaak het. Die 52 bladsye boek bevat ook 'n dagboek van die gebeure, inkleurprente en 5 kolgansaktiwiteite. <br></strong><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMTI2ND9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--4f8a12df6b3d85c006a5fcf22aaab2d9c43c6f0f" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdkFFIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--c2ca2e3945a83021e2aab69459cdab12d3e61943/kopieerboeke.png" filename="kopieerboeke.png" filesize="99215" width="582" height="408" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Kopieerboeke"></action-text-attachment><strong><br>My </strong><a href="https://lomi.co.za/kopieerboeke/"><strong>kopieerboeke</strong></a><strong> bevat nie net kopieerwerk nie, maar hope aktiwiteite om handvaardigheid te bevorder. Dit bevat teksverse, gedigte en ander inligting om dit 'n leersame ervaring saam met die pret te maak. <br><br>Loer gerus ook in by my 11 jarige se </strong><a href="https://lomi.co.za/salomie-se-storiehoekie/"><strong>storiehoekie</strong></a><strong> waar sy haar stories luisterstories verkoop. <br></strong><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvODIzP2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--e88c6f7bad9743a3943257432427eb59b3b3ab91" content-type="application/pdf" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBamNEIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--bd6e9be534341be71a3f43cd72ede397ee71083e/Lomi%20katalogus%20Afrikaans%20Jul20.pdf" filename="Lomi katalogus Afrikaans Jul20.pdf" filesize="2903308"></action-text-attachment><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvODI1P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--82747ddb38bb5066c99a3d473a8ddfe13e0a0736" content-type="application/pdf" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBamtEIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--a8286a2647d4625c053932412964d8d2dacb0d13/Salomie%20se%20storiehoekie.pdf" filename="Salomie se storiehoekie.pdf" filesize="1065735"></action-text-attachment><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMTI3MD9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--0fa7f0d2758ab4cccc75ecf1f85ee184a170ae24" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdllFIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--a5dbbb9ed1d94c016f0bb43963a6f4a3feaace94/Number%20Addventure.png" filename="Number Addventure.png" filesize="174512" width="587" height="514" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Number Ad(d)venture Series"></action-text-attachment><em>The idea behind the Number Ad(d)venture series is to make maths fun for children. Children shouldn't use a book and think I must be able to do everything or that it is aimed at younger children. It is meant to be fun – to show children that maths isn’t boring. For this reason the books are not grade-specific. </em><br><em>Each book does cover some skills, which are aimed at a specific grade. The series is however there to help build maths proficiency in a fun away. Each book in the series also includes activities that are not curriculum-based and which are aimed at developing problem-solving skills. <br><br></em><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI-Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvMTI3ND9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiDHB1cnBvc2UGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFRJIg9leHBpcmVzX2F0BjsAVDA=--8028ab833e95d02bdf36272f1c7e25c32aca8137" content-type="image/png" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdm9FIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--a9d13d48b7bceadaf1d893779f1192e5d9d3119d/fun%20packs.png" filename="fun packs.png" filesize="113673" width="710" height="426" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="Fun Packs"></action-text-attachment><em><br>Besides the Number Ad(d)venture series there is also a variety of activity packs with specific themes (Spring, Robots) and game packs. These fun packs can be added alongside any curriculum to break the </em>monotony<em> of worksheet work. </em></div><div><br><strong><em>Also, have a peek at my 11 year old’s </em></strong><a href="https://lomi.co.za/salomie-se-storiehoekie/"><strong><em>story corner</em></strong></a><strong><em> where she sells her Afrikaans audio stories. </em></strong></div><div><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSI9Z2lkOi8vZXZlbnRzLXBsYXRmb3JtL0FjdGl2ZVN0b3JhZ2U6OkJsb2IvODI0P2V4cGlyZXNfaW4GOwBUSSIMcHVycG9zZQY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVEkiD2V4cGlyZXNfYXQGOwBUMA==--547871efd6ae4ee7d4528bfef5c99745b97fa985" content-type="application/pdf" url="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/files/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBamdEIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--0c6a52c6e3f6677bd9bc5b2923021a505df95187/Lomi%20catalog%20English.pdf" filename="Lomi catalog English.pdf" filesize="1120921"></action-text-attachment></div>	Company	34	2020-09-17 08:27:22.37068	2020-10-03 19:13:18.596187
