fidently.<br> Pilots   will   receive   both   theoretical   and   practical   training   to   increasing   their knowledge and skill in operating a drone safely and responsibly.<br><br></div><div>This course aims to provide you with a broad overview of the drone industry, the regulatory environment in which to operate as well as the technical aspects of drones/ Remotely Piloted Aircraft Systems (RPAS).  Most importantly, the purpose of this course is to provide you with the skills and confidence to fly your drone and have fun!<br><br><strong>Inspire Agricultural Drone Competency Course</strong><br>Drone technology is giving the agriculture industry a high-technology makeover, with planning and strategy based on real-time data gathering and processing.<br><br>Drones are enabling farmers to greatly increase efficiency in certain farming processes. From livestock management to crop monitoring, planting, irrigation mapping, security and more!</div><div><br>Our Agricultural Drone Flying Competency Course not only gives you all the training you need to safely operate a multi-rotor drone, but also provides a theoretical and practical introduction to drone applications in your industry, as well as comprehensive flight training by our professional drone pilots.<br><br></div><div><br><br></div>	Company	76	2020-10-09 20:12:44.756238	2020-10-12 10:39:28.160872
