cific workshop, you can click on it's Zoom link. The link will only be available during the time that is shown.</li><li>If you have missed the workshop you will still be able to view a recording of the workshop for the rest of the duration of the expo.  </li></ul></li><li><strong>Exhibitors</strong><ul><li>For the duration of the expo you will be able to visit the online stalls of all companies exhibiting at the event.</li><li>You can see a list of exhibitors by clicking on the Exhibitors tab on the main menu or on the green block on the Home page that says Exhibitors.</li><li>By hovering your mouse over an exhibitor flip card you are able to see a short description of the exhibitor's product offerings. </li><li>During the expo a blue bar with the word <strong>Show</strong> appears beneath each exhibitor card. Clicking on this bar will take you to a page containing the exhibitor's stall.</li><li>At the bottom of the exhibitor's stall, there is a green menu bar giving you access to the different sections of the exhibitor's stall.</li><li>You can ask the exhibitor questions, with the Live Chat feature in each stall.</li></ul></li></ul>	Event	1	2020-08-16 12:47:08.077863	2020-10-14 17:08:03.468985
