tbooks at publishers' prices</h1><div><br></div><h1><strong>Join a free online consultation and trial our platform.</strong></h1><h1><br></h1><h1>We invite you to attend an online consultation with a member of our academic team to find out how our platform works and to ask any questions you have.<br><br>Please email us at: admin@globalvillageint.com or use the "Chat with us" function at the bottom right hand side of the screen (above "Let's Chat") to arrange an online consultation and to trial our Classroom.<br><br>You will receive an email invitation to the meeting and confirmation of your meeting time.  <br><br>We look forward to speaking with you!</h1><div><br></div><h1><strong>Course Options<br><br>BASIC COMPONENTS included in all our courses:</strong><br> <strong>Access to our Google Classroom 30 Week blended learning course</strong> includes:<br> curriculum aligned course material <br>specially designed activities <br>infographics <br>relevant video lessons <br>carefully selected &amp; appropriate internet links <br><strong>5 Sets of marked assignments for each subject</strong> with tutor feedback <br><strong>Past papers with memorandums</strong> <strong>3 Progress transcripts</strong> to track your child’s progress</h1><h1><strong> <br>We offer the following options:<br></strong><br></h1><h1><strong>3 Learn at Your Own Pace options </strong><em>and</em></h1><h1><strong>1 Timetabled CLASSES option<br></strong><br></h1><h1><strong>3 LEARN AT YOUR OWN PACE OPTIONS</strong></h1><h1>Enrol any time of year<br><br><strong>Option 1: KEY   <br></strong>The KEY course includes all the basic components.<br><br></h1><h1><strong>Option 2: CORE  <br></strong>The CORE course includes all the basic components <strong>plus:</strong></h1><h1>Entry assessments<strong> </strong></h1><h1>An individual introductory coaching session with your Academic Coach</h1><h1>Pre-exam tutoring meeting for each subject with our subject specialist tutors.  <br><br></h1><h1><strong>Option 3: COACH</strong></h1><h1>The <strong>COACH </strong>course includes all the components of the CORE course plus:</h1><h1>A weekly academic coaching session with your Academic Coach.  </h1><h1><strong> </strong></h1><h1><strong>TIMETABLED CLASSES<br></strong>The CLASS option is ideal for students who prefer the structure of weekly scheduled lessons.  Classes start in January 2021.<br><br></h1><h1><strong>CLASS  <br></strong>The <strong>CLASS</strong> includes all the basic components <strong>plus:</strong></h1><h1>An introductory online meeting with your Academic Coach<br>Weekly scheduled group online tutoring classes.<br><br><strong>Fees<br></strong>Courses for Primary from R1 500 pm  <br>Courses for Stage 7, 8 and 9 from R1 500 pm<br>Courses for International GCSE from R2 100 pm<br>Courses for AS Level from R1 145 pm</h1><div><strong> </strong><br><br></div><div><strong><br></strong><br></div><div><br><br></div>	Company	71	2020-10-08 10:35:29.597132	2020-10-17 08:24:24.145204
