530	introduction	<div>Die volle program is beskikbaar in beide Afrikaans en Engels. Gebruikers kan tussen die taalkeuses wissel.<br><br></div><div>The YouCanDoScience program was developed with distance learning in mind, for both Afrikaans and English learners - it is your own, private online Physical Science teacher. <br><br></div><div>The program is made up of 300+ video lessons of 10-20 minute duration, each developing new concepts in detail from ground principles, just like a teacher would do in a school period. Learners can stop, start and rewind the lesson as many times as is needed to suit their individual learning pace. Lessons contain numerous systematically worked out examples.<br><br></div><div>Each video is followed by a short test, which is instantly marked by the computer, for the learners to immediately see whether they did understand the concepts that were discussed in the lesson. A summary of notes also comes with each lesson<br><br></div><div>There are also revision lessons, which are ideally suited for revision just before a test series or exams. As the name indicates, known concepts are revisited and emphasised, not developed again.<br><br></div><div>Because Physical Science is a practical subject that must be understood rather than simply being learned, it must be stressed that the success of the program lies in the degree of interactivity of the learner with the lesson. Learners must stop, rewind and restart lessons till they fully grasp a concept and continuously make their own notes to make sure that concepts are firmly entrenched. After a problem is given in a lesson, the video should be stopped and learners must attempt to do the problem on their own first, before listening to the detailed explanation and comparing it with their own attempt. Learners who only passively listen to the lessons will not get the full benefit of the program.<br><br></div><div>The program is ideally suited for the home schooler wishing to do Physical Science, although students must find an establishment where they can write their exams.<br><br></div><div>For more info visit our website <a href="https://youcandoscience.co.za/">https://youcandoscience.co.za/</a></div>	Company	73	2020-10-08 14:07:28.769742	2020-10-13 11:24:29.53833
