585	info_desk	<h1><strong>Enquiries during the expo</strong></h1><div><br>Welcome to our expo <strong>Info Desk</strong>. We would like to assist you with any enquiries on the expo that you may have. There are different ways in which we will be<br>able to assist you:<br><br><strong>Watch the video</strong></div><ul><li>After you have watched the <a href="https://youtu.be/XDIvsI3lDQw"><strong><em>welcoming video of Bouwe van der Eems</em></strong></a>, we strongly recommend that you watch the <a href="https://youtu.be/SDdxQaldJ0Y"><strong><em>Visitor´s Information expo guide video</em></strong></a> in which Sone will shortly explain to you how to navigate through the expo, how to search for the most relevant information applicable to your preferences, and in general<br>to just make you feel at ease in this cyber expo world.</li></ul><div><br><strong>Read the FAQ</strong></div><ul><li>To get an overview on how the Home Education Expo is structured, how to find your way through the expo and how to make the most of the event we also recommend that you consider reading through the <a href="http://homeschoolexpo.africa/events/1/faq"><strong><em>FAQ</em></strong></a>.</li></ul><div><br><strong>Type chat with us</strong></div><ul><li>We are available from 9:00 to 17:00 every expo day to answer your more specific questions. Just type in your questions and we will respond instantly. After hours you are still welcome to leave us a text message on which we will respond at the soonest. You will find our green <strong>Info Desk</strong> <strong>Chat box</strong> in the bottom left corner on the <a href="http://www.homeschoolexpo.africa/events/1"><strong><em>Home page</em></strong></a>.</li></ul><div><br><strong>Zoom chat with us</strong></div><ul><li>We know that one can converse only so much by typing and then the need arises to rather speak verbally to someone. For this purpose we have set up a Zoom reception that you may enter at any time during office hours to speak to any of our <strong>Info Desk</strong> assistants. <a href="https://zoom.us/j/3202541524?pwd=c3A2dTdJSm9FWENPVFREMUFETkR6Zz09"><strong><em>CLICK HERE</em></strong></a> to talk to us.</li></ul>	Event	1	2020-10-10 11:45:47.689954	2020-10-13 20:02:10.534005
